Yek '''kher''' (vay '''khâr''') si yek than kay beshen tay  jipen le manusha, kerdo te garuvel len katar [[brishind]], [[balval]], [[tatipen]], [[shil]] vai biamala. Si les zidurya (pashavre), uchhardo tay  yek vay buteder livnya (kherkotora, sobe, besharnya). Les si les yek vay buteder udara, pale varesave purane khera (sar kay [[Chatalhöyük]]) labyarden uchharde tay shopnya te den andre. Vi si les dikhavne (filyastre) te del andre o [[Kham]]esko dud tay  te dikhel pes avri.

O lav si [[Indo-Aryano]] ([[Hindi]]: घर - ghâr).

